Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.97,0:00:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Celestia: It is time\Nfor us to retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.21,0:00:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And you want ME\Nto take your place?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.58,0:00:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,With the help of\Nyour friends, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You may call\Nme.. Grogar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Together, Equestria\Nwill be ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.22,0:00:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sombra: I will take back the\NCrystal Empire on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.66,0:00:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike: How are we\Ngoing to stop them?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.09,0:00:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight: With the\NElements of Harmony!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.73,0:00:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,With those, we can\Ndefeat anypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.31,0:01:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What. Just. Happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.95,0:01:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tree of Harmony can't\Nreally be gone, can it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.05,0:01:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.36,0:01:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But it is! You thought\Nyou'd defeated me,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.06,0:01:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but you led\Nme right to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.49,0:01:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the source of\Nyour power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.43,0:01:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that it's\Ndestroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.46,0:01:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing can stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.67,0:01:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right. With\Nthe Elements gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.44,0:01:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how\Nwe can defeat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll just have to beat\Nhim the old-fashioned way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.83,0:02:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.17,0:02:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! You're no match for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.47,0:02:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I will finally rule\Nthe Crystal Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.81,0:02:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. With you out of the way,\NI will rule all of Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.75,0:02:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.55,0:02:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. And I think I know\Nexactly where I'll start!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.52,0:02:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.35,0:02:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Your sweet little home town.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.76,0:02:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You leave Ponyville alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.06,0:02:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.26,0:02:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Without your Elements, it would\Nbe so easy to control you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's no point,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.30,0:02:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,my conquering Ponyville is\Nalready your greatest fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.61,0:02:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.64,0:02:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.22,0:03:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. The Tree of\NHarmony grew the Elements;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.15,0:03:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,it kept the Everfree\NForest under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.65,0:03:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And now it's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.99,0:03:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sombra will take\Nover Equestria,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I wasn't ready to\Ntake the Princesses' place,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.10,0:03:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but I never thought\NI'd mess up this badly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you\Nlooking at me for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.70,0:03:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is usually when\Nyou say something funny
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.71,0:03:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to lift our spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, nothing about\Nthis is funny to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I'm\Ntrying to be strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,but I just can't bear to think\Nabout poor Sweetie Belle
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.08,0:03:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,under the spell\Nof that monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Or those sweet\Nlittle Cake twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.85,0:03:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Or Spike or Starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.12,0:03:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Or Angel or anypony forced\Nto do that monster's bidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.60,0:03:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What the--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.73,0:03:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.63,0:03:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't just stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.47,0:03:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a plan and I don't\Nknow what I'm going to do
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:03:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,once we get out, but\Nwe can't just sit here
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and let Sombra make slaves\Nof every pony we love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me help. I'm faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.81,0:04:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I like digging!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.92,0:04:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been known to\Nget my hooves dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Move over, y'all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.22,0:04:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally I wouldn't dream\Nof digging, but right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me the muddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.44,0:04:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.48,0:04:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me. Look at\Nme, sugarcube!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, you gotta\Nfree her! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.83,0:04:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I-can't. Without\Nthe Elements,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.16,0:04:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,my magic isn't strong\Nenough to stop Sombra's!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, where are you\Ngoing? Starlight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.17,0:05:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[robotic] We must lay siege to Canterlot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Snap out of it, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.11,0:05:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're stronger than his magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity: Sweetie\NBelle, please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.22,0:05:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get her to stop.\NI can't get her to--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,None of us can. We\Ncan't reach them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.03,0:05:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He made them bake a black\Nlicorice fruitcake that says
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,"Congratulations to our\Nfavorite Supreme Emperor,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,King Sombra!" in\Ngreen frosting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,IT'S THE UGLIEST\NCAKE I'VE EVER SEEN!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.08,0:05:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, this is\Nbad. Like really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.55,0:05:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been so\Nsad in my whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to do. I\Ndon't know how to free them
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.65,0:05:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't know\Nhow to stop Sombra!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony was so sure\NI'd do such a great job!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.49,0:05:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is exactly\Nwhat I was afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.63,0:06:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Could anything else\Npossibly go wrong!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, with the Tree\Nof Harmony gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the Everfree Forest\Ncould grow out of control
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.97,0:06:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and threaten the town!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling, that's\Noddly specific.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we figure out\Nhow to defeat Sombra
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.12,0:06:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and bring everypony\Nback to Ponyville,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,if we don't stop the forest,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,there won't be a\NPonyville to come back to!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.36,0:06:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow: Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,For our friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,For our families.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,For our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,For Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All: Equestriaaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You! Break it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.01,0:07:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They've fled. Celestia\Nand Luna are too cowardly
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.15,0:07:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,to even stand against\Nme. Equestria is MINE!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.88,0:07:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, everypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been at this for hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.99,0:08:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's just growin'\Nback too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to keep trying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I know we're supposed to\Nbe able to handle things
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.84,0:08:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,on our own, but I've\Nnever been happier
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,to see two ponies\Nin my whole life!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.04,0:08:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[zap] Nopony is meant to\Nhandle this on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.35,0:08:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Starswirl! The Tree\Nof Harmony, it's--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.48,0:08:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. I alerted the\Nprincesses as soon as I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.22,0:08:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt it, when it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.19,0:08:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Like part of my essence\Njust ceased to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what you mean. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be. I've more\Nthan enough magic in me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.13,0:08:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to keep the Everfree\NForest under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.73,0:08:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.77,0:08:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The Pillars and I planted\Nthe Tree of Harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:08:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think kept\Nthe Forest under control
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,before it did?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.94,0:09:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It will take time,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.28,0:09:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,but with the Princesses'\Nhelp, I can keep it at bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.52,0:09:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, yeah! Go get 'em, Beardy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.53,0:09:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sombra's back and he's taken\Ncontrol of all of our friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.20,0:09:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We've left Canterlot\Ndefenseless!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.80,0:09:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, you must\Ngo! Defend Equestria
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and we shall\Ncontain the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.08,0:09:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,At least now we're back\Nto just one problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.16,0:09:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, everypony's all evil-y.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sombra's going\Nto force us
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.29,0:09:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to fight our way\Nthrough our friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.56,0:09:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Not if I can help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. Guess we need a\Ndifferent plan. Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know! I'm not\Nprepared to fight against
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.15,0:10:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the citizens of Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's one more\Nthing I'm not ready to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we'd better figure\Nout something quick
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.26,0:10:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,because none of them seem\Nto have a problem with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.87,0:10:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh! Sorry about this, Fancy Pants!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.65,0:10:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We promise we'll let y'all\Nout as soon as we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.28,0:10:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I go here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.45,0:10:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Or here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.29,0:10:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Or here or there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.16,0:10:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.37,0:11:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.54,0:11:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how long\Nwe can hold them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.38,0:11:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And holding them off\Nisn't what we need anyhow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.58,0:11:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to get inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.18,0:11:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't just\Nleave them here,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.98,0:11:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,all possessed and Sombrafied.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.09,0:11:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do, Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.92,0:11:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, but\Nwe can't stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.69,0:11:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry we couldn't\Nhelp our friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but I didn't know\Nwhat else to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,At least we're inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.10,0:11:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. All we have to do\Nnow is defeat King Sombra. [nervous chuckle]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I-- we--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.11,0:11:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my. No Elements?\NNo princesses?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.51,0:11:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like you're in\Na bit of a pickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.01,0:11:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Or are you in [snap]\Nmore of a jam?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.59,0:12:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Discord! What are\Nyou doing here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.62,0:12:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I was going to hang\Nthese up all over the castle
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.76,0:12:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to celebrate your coronation,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.86,0:12:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but apparently, it's\Na bit premature.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.90,0:12:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.57,0:12:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We could really use\Nsome all-powerful
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.10,0:12:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord of Chaos' help right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Moi? Oh, I couldn't possibly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.31,0:12:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, poodles!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.95,0:12:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Discord, {\i1}please{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.15,0:12:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh. Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.49,0:12:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to be clear, I was really\Nrooting for you to do this
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,on your own and parlay\Nthat confidence boost
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.60,0:12:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,into being the best Protectors\Nof Equestria you can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.87,0:12:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A little less talking and\Na little more helping!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.84,0:12:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Thank you, Discord!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.94,0:12:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what\Nwe'd do without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.02,0:13:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, "King" Sombra. Time\Nto give up the crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.16,0:13:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Here to fight the good fight\Nwith nothing but your wits?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Admirable, but foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.91,0:13:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it's on\Nme to be the MVP today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.38,0:13:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I was betting on you, and\NI do hate being wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.88,0:13:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Although if you think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.35,0:13:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I am your friend so maybe you\Nwin because friendship wins?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.82,0:13:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Although Fluttershy should\Nget most of the credit for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.69,0:13:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She's my favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] Discord!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.31,0:14:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even the Lord of Chaos\Ncan stand against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.71,0:14:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I am truly the most powerful\Ncreature in Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.32,0:14:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Discord!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.85,0:14:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We need you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Please wake up. Please wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.26,0:14:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] Discord!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.06,0:14:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you're OK. We\Ncan't beat him without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.77,0:14:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You couldn't beat\Nme with him either!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.40,0:14:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It would appear that\Nyou're on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.54,0:14:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing left to give..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.61,0:14:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it then. We're doomed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.32,0:14:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it's taken\Nyou this long to realize it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.92,0:14:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, how shall I\Neliminate all this clutter
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,in my throne room?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.90,0:14:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me. You don't need me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:14:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need the princesses
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and you certainly don't\Nneed the Elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, you will\Nalways be kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.14,0:15:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack, you will\Nalways be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.04,0:15:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity, you'll\Nalways be generous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And Rainbow Dash will\Nbe loyal as can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.38,0:15:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie will always bring\Nlaughter wherever she goes
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.76,0:15:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and Twilight, [wheeze] you are\Nand always will be
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.49,0:15:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the embodiment of Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.56,0:15:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You lost sight of\Nwhat's in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here, together,\Nwilling to give
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.90,0:15:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,everything you've\Ngot for Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.84,0:15:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing and no pony can ever\Ntake that away from you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.08,0:15:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,because that's who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to take more\Nthan a sentimental speech
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.75,0:15:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.65,0:15:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Discord's right. We've\Nproven time and time again
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:16:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that the real magic is the\Nsix of us working together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.96,0:16:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,With these girls by my\Nside, I'm not afraid of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.20,0:16:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not afraid of what you can\Ndo or how much power you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You may knock us down, but we're\Ngoing to get back up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.21,0:16:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And again. As long\Nas we're together,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.55,0:16:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,we will never stop\Ntrying to defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,For our friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.79,0:16:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,For our families.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.96,0:16:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,For our Home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,For Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No! This can't be possible!\NYour magic can't defeat mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.54,0:16:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I destroyed the\Nsource of your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.64,0:16:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't destroy our\Nfriendship, Sombra.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.51,0:16:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And we keep telling bad guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:17:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But y'all just don't\Nseem to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.59,0:17:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendship IS magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.26,0:17:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Noooooooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.55,0:17:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! Do you want more juice?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.45,0:17:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Only if it's not too much\Ntrouble, and it's red,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.39,0:17:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and it has one of those little\Numbrellas, and two cherries.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No no. Actually make it three.\NAnd maybe..... some doughnuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.23,0:17:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you've made\Nyourselves at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Celestia! Luna! I know\Nwhat you're going to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.84,0:17:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have called on\Nyou as soon as I knew
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,how dangerous it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A good leader knows when to\Nask for help and I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.85,0:18:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And because of me, the Tree\Nof Harmony was destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.28,0:18:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Equestria deserves somepony\Nmuch better than me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,as its leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,About one thing. A good leader\Nknows when to ask for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.63,0:18:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But a great leader has\Nthe courage to admit
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,when they've\Nmade a mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.00,0:18:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and the strength\Nto make it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.57,0:18:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, you've proven to\Nme beyond any doubt,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.44,0:18:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,that you will be a\Ngreat leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.94,0:18:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Will be?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Luna and I have decided\Nit may have been
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.78,0:18:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,a bit unfair to thrust\Nthis upon you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.41,0:18:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,without giving you the\Ntime you need to prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.28,0:18:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank goodness! I\Nreally wasn't ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.05,0:18:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Not ready!? So Twilight's\Nnot taking over?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.69,0:18:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This was all for nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.16,0:18:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I pretended to be\Nvery hurt and gave
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.39,0:18:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,one of the most convincing\Nspeeches of-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.53,0:18:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,PRETENDED?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.63,0:18:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. You don't\Nthink some would-be-king
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,could actually hurt the\NLord of Chaos, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:19:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, as I was saying, I\Npretended to be very hurt
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.37,0:19:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,to convince you that\Nyou didn't need anything
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.84,0:19:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,but yourself to be\Nthe incredible leader
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you can be! And\Nnow it's not happening!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.88,0:19:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It will, but when she's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How can she not be ready!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.59,0:19:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What a waste of a perfectly\Nwonderful speech!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Honestly, I don't know\Nwhy I even bother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! So he could have ended\Nthe whole Sombra thing
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.33,0:19:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,whenever he wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.83,0:19:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But he didn't because he cares.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.87,0:19:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Discord for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.37,0:19:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He sure has a weird way\Nof being supportive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Super odd dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.61,0:19:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.52,0:19:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, truth be told, Celestia\Nand I had fun today,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.89,0:19:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,fighting side-by-side with\NStarswirl for our home!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.86,0:19:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been years since we've\Ngotten to do what you girls do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.73,0:19:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You all make it look so easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.43,0:19:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we are kind of\Nan awesome team.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.77,0:20:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Every adventure\Nis heart-pounding
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but so rewarding!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.77,0:20:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm up for anything, as long\Nas it's with all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.61,0:20:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Life certainly hasn't\Nbeen dull since we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nowhere else I'd rather be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.38,0:20:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We are pretty\Nincredible together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.38,0:20:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And we would do\Nanything for Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I know,\Nwhen the time comes,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.55,0:20:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,as long as we're\Ntogether, we probably--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,--we definitely got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.20,0:20:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I'll say something\Nnice about centaurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.63,0:20:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Tirek, you say something\Nnice about changelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.74,0:20:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And Chrysalis, you say\Nsomething nice about ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.41,0:20:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,NEVER!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us hope the three of you\Nwill be enough for my plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.52,0:20:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And what of King Sombra?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.58,0:20:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he succeed?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.72,0:20:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,HA!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.79,0:21:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say he gambled and lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.57,0:21:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But at least he can\Nserve as a warning
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.57,0:21:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,to those who doubt\Ncontinuing with my plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.67,0:21:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless any of you have doubts...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.47,0:21:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. Not I.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.11,0:21:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.71,0:21:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.64,0:21:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we shall join\Nforces and work together
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.78,0:21:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,to bring Equestria\Nto its knees!
